title: S15 Ep56: Supernatural News/Parashare: It's Just The Dog Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: It's Just The Dog Edition
description:
Darkness Radio has Supernatural News/Parashare: It's Just The Dog Edition!

You have kept asking us to replay this gem of a Parashare show, and we have acquiesced! This episode of Parashare originally aired January 5, 2015 and featured Eric and Tammy from a local video crew who wanted to video stream Dave and Tim while they did Supernatural News/Parashare, and the boys decide to make their case as to why it probably isn't such a good idea!

Sit back and laugh along at the absurdity of WHERE this episode goes eventually!

Get your awesome Paranormal needs met here: https://www.amazon.com/shop/darknessradiodave
